  2. label - critical

    Ensures every form element has a label

    Form elements must have labels

    • aria-label : aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty

      aria-labelledby : aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty or not visible

      implicit-label : Form element does not have an implicit (wrapped)

      explicit-label : Form element does not have an explicit

      non-empty-title : Element has no title attribute or the title attribute is empty

      #Form > input[type="text"][name="question"]

  4. label - critical

    Ensures every form element has a label

    Form elements must have labels

    • aria-label : aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty

      aria-labelledby : aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty or not visible

      implicit-label : Form element does not have an implicit (wrapped)

      explicit-label : Form element does not have an explicit

      non-empty-title : Element has no title attribute or the title attribute is empty

      #Form > input[type="text"][name="question"]

    tags: cat.forms wcag2a wcag332 wcag131 section508 section508.22.n

  5. link-name - serious

    Ensures links have discernible text

    Links must have discernible text

    • has-visible-text : Element does not have text that is visible to screen readers

      aria-label : aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty

      aria-labelledby : aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty or not visible

      role-presentation : Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="presentation"

      role-none : Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="none"

      #departmentalSocialNav > a[href$="UTSAadvising"]

  3. label - critical

    Ensures every form element has a label

    Form elements must have labels

    • aria-label : aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty

      aria-labelledby : aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty or not visible

      implicit-label : Form element does not have an implicit (wrapped)

      explicit-label : Form element does not have an explicit

      non-empty-title : Element has no title attribute or the title attribute is empty
